<div class="divright">
<h2>Welcome To Bright Angels School</h2>
	<div class="box2">
	Bright Angels School has been founded by Major and Mrs. Hussain in the year 2002, who understands the actual  sense of serving country through noble profession i.e. mould and prepare young minds in shaping the bright future of our Nation, with the aim to provide children with a sound foundation of broad based education in an atmosphere free from inhibition and prejudices in order to promote the full development of the children (physical, mental & moral) and to prepare them for a bright future.<div class="line"></div>
<p>
<h3>Mission/Vision</h3>
<div class="clear" style="height:10px;"> Bright Angels School aims at the integral, personalized education of the child. It strives to produce intellectually well trained, morally upright, socially committed, spiritually inspired men and women, who can contribute to the development of our nation and remain good citizens.<br />
<a href="mission-vision.php" class="more">More...</a>
	</div>

